title: Wide Receiver & Running Back Combine Preview
itunes:title: Wide Receiver & Running Back Combine Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, DJ gives the average combine numbers of some of the wide receivers in the league (1:14). After, the guys preview the wide receivers that will be at the combine and discuss what they're looking forward to seeing from them (5:41). To wrap up the show, the pair preview the running backs at the combine and talk about what to expect from them (16:27).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
